	<h1>
		OKF KnowledgeForge Project
	</h1>
	
	<st:Section>
		<h2>
			Overview
		</h2>
		<p>
			KnowledgeForge (KForge) is a digitally-based open knowledge community. The KnowledgeForge project works to provide the resources and technological infrastructure to give KForge life. The KForge system itself enables a self sustaining community to create works of intellectual and artistic value. KnowledgeForge is one of the core projects of the <a href="http://www.openknowledgefoundation.org/">Open Knowledge Foundation</a>. To find out more:
		</p>
		<ul>
			<li>
				See the in depth <a href="overview.html">Overview</a>
			</li>
			<li>
				Understand the project's background and motivation by reading <a href="http://www.openknowledgefoundation.org/why_the_okf.html">Why the OKF?</a>
			</li>
			<li>
				Check out the beta site <a href="http://www.kforge.net/">www.kforge.net</a>
			</li>
			<li>
				Read the <a href="wiki/">wiki</a>
			</li>
		</ul>
	</st:Section>
	
